===How Can I Change the NetBeans Splash Screen Shown When A User Installs a Module Requiring Restart?===

The splash screen is here:

<pre>autoupdate.services/libsrc/org/netbeans/updater/resources/updatersplash.gif</pre>

You can brand this in your application; see: [[BrandingUpdaterSplash]]

----
Applies to: NetBeans 6.5 and later

